{"run_id": "052c70280bb9", "query": "If I invest $5000 at 6% annual interest compounded monthly for 7 years, what is the final balance?", "final_answer": "The final balance after 7 years would be **$7,601.85**.\n\nThis means your investment would grow by $2,601.85 in interest over the 7-year period.", "total_input_tokens": 2617, "total_output_tokens": 207, "started_at": 1778548642.707432, "ended_at": 1778548648.2447019, "duration_sec": 5.537269830703735, "events": [{"kind": "user", "elapsed_ms": 0.0, "timestamp": 1778548642.707438, "data": {"text": "If I invest $5000 at 6% annual interest compounded monthly for 7 years, what is the final balance?"}}, {"kind": "model", "elapsed_ms": 3144.0162658691406, "timestamp": 1778548645.851464, "data": {"step": 0, "stop_reason": "tool_use", "content": [{"citations": null, "text": "I'll calculate the final balance using the compound interest formula.\n\nFor compound interest, the formula is:\nA = P(1 + r/n)^(nt)\n\nWhere:\n- P = principal ($5000)\n- r = annual interest rate (0.06)\n- n = number of times compounded per year (12 for monthly)\n- t = time in years (7)", "type": "text"}, {"id": "toolu_01Xk5g5Ccsd5j5uUUXVbB4SP", "caller": {"type": "direct"}, "input": {"expression": "5000 * (1 + 0.06/12)**(12*7)"}, "name": "calculator_tool", "type": "tool_use"}], "input_tokens": 1202, "output_tokens": 161}}, {"kind": "tool_use", "elapsed_ms": 0.0, "timestamp": 1778548645.851467, "data": {"name": "calculator_tool", "input": {"expression": "5000 * (1 + 0.06/12)**(12*7)"}, "tool_use_id": "toolu_01Xk5g5Ccsd5j5uUUXVbB4SP"}}, {"kind": "tool_result", "elapsed_ms": 0.04673004150390625, "timestamp": 1778548645.851516, "data": {"tool_name": "calculator_tool", "tool_use_id": "toolu_01Xk5g5Ccsd5j5uUUXVbB4SP", "result": {"ok": true, "expression": "5000 * (1 + 0.06/12)**(12*7)", "result": 7601.848180410409}}}, {"kind": "model", "elapsed_ms": 2393.138885498047, "timestamp": 1778548648.2446852, "data": {"step": 1, "stop_reason": "end_turn", "content":